Overview of former and current Takin repositories
-------------------------------------------------

- From 2019 till now:
	https://code.ill.fr/scientific-software/takin
	Main development repository group for Takin 2.

- From 2016 till 2019:
	https://github.com/t-weber/takin
	Private repository for Takin 1.

- From 2014 till 2017:
	https://forge.frm2.tum.de/cgit/cgit.cgi/frm2/mira/tastools.git/
	Former main development repository for Takin 1.


